data.description: Welcome to 219 Ambridge Ave, a 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home nestled in the Quaker Valley School District. Situated just minutes from Sewickley/Ambridge, residents of 219 Ambridge Ave enjoy the convenience of being close to a variety of grocery stores and shops that are within easy reach. The kitchen is an open space equipped with modern stainless steel appliances and french doors that lead to your very own private oasis! Don't let the yucky weather fool you because Spring/Summer are right around the corner! One of the standout features of this property is the expansive backyard. Step outside to discover a private paradise with an above ground pool, inviting hot tub, and two serene ponds. The large fenced-in yard provides a secure and tranquil space for outdoor activities and gatherings. Multiple parking spaces available in the front and back as well as the detached 30x32 garage. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Quaker Valley gem your own – schedule a showing today!
